@startuml
title pg:: battle phase system (battle.md §2 — port of Unity proposition.md)
hide empty members

interface IBattlePhase {
  +enter() / tick(dt) / exit()
}
class BattleOrchestrator {
  -current : IBattlePhase*
  +transitionTo(phase)
  .. dumb state machine: never decides next ..
}
class BattleCoordinator {
  -context : BattleContext&
  -phases (created up front)
  .. owns transition rules; reads context;
     injects pending BattleAction into Resolution ..
}
class SetupPhase
class PlacementPhase {
  +onPlacementFinished : signal
}
class IdlePhase {
  .. advance turn bars to next ready (D23),
     select unit (player-side tie-break), beginTurn ..
  +onUnitReady : signal
}
class PlayerTurnPhase {
  .. binds battle input on enter, unbinds on exit ..
  +onActionChosen : signal<BattleAction>
}
class EnemyTurnPhase {
  .. AI evaluation → legal action or EndTurn ..
  +onActionChosen : signal<BattleAction>
}
class ResolutionPhase {
  -pending : BattleAction
  +onResolved : signal
}
class EndPhase {
  .. BattleWon events, battleResolved ..
}
IBattlePhase <|.. SetupPhase
IBattlePhase <|.. PlacementPhase
IBattlePhase <|.. IdlePhase
IBattlePhase <|.. PlayerTurnPhase
IBattlePhase <|.. EnemyTurnPhase
IBattlePhase <|.. ResolutionPhase
IBattlePhase <|.. EndPhase
BattleOrchestrator o-- IBattlePhase
BattleCoordinator o-- BattleOrchestrator
BattleCoordinator ..> IBattlePhase : creates & wires signals

package "rules (static, stateless)" {
  class BattleTurnRules
  class BattleActionValidator
  class BattleActionResolver
  class BattleStatusRules
  class BattleResourceRules
  class BattleOutcomeRules
  class BattlePlacementRules
  class LineOfSight
}
IdlePhase ..> BattleTurnRules
ResolutionPhase ..> BattleActionValidator
ResolutionPhase ..> BattleActionResolver
PlacementPhase ..> BattlePlacementRules
BattleCoordinator ..> BattleOutcomeRules

note as N1
Setup → Placement → Idle → PlayerTurn|EnemyTurn
  → Resolution → (same turn continues | endTurn → Idle)
  → ... → End
end note
@enduml
